Asylum decisions taken on asylum claims of asylum-seekers

asylum_decisions.Rd

Data collated by UNHCR about asylum decisions taken on asylum claims of asylum-seekers residing in World. Data is available since 2000.

asylum_decisions

Format

A data frame with 82486 rows and 16 variables:

Year

character Year

CountryOriginCode

character Country of Origin Code isoA3

CountryAsylumCode

character Country of Asylum Code isoA3

CountryOriginName

character Country of Origin Name

CountryAsylumName

character Country of Asylum Name

ProcedureType

character Procedure Type

ProcedureName

character Procedure Name

DecisionTypeCode

character Decision Type Code

DecisionDataType

character Decision Data Type

DecisionData

character Decision Data

DecisionsAveragePersonsPerCase

integer Decisions Average Persons Per Case

Recognized

integer Recognized

ComplementaryProtection

integer Complementary Protection

OtherwiseClosed

integer Otherwise Closed

Rejected

integer Rejected

Total Decided

integer Total Decided

Source

https://data.humdata.org/dataset/unhcr-population-data-for-world
